uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.ControllerImpl

Class ReferencedIdentificationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.ControllerImpl.AbstractDataAccessController
      • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.ControllerImpl.CachedDataAccessController
        • uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller.impl.ControllerImpl.ReferencedIdentificationController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetaDataAccess, MzGraphDataAccess, PeptideDataAccess, ProteinDataAccess, ProteinGroupDataAccess, QuantDataAccess, DataAccessController
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MzIdentMLControllerImpl, MzTabControllerImpl

    public abstract class ReferencedIdentificationController
extends CachedDataAccessController
    Abstract Class that contains methods shared by mzTab controller and mzIdentML controller and also some data structures share for both classes. This class is specialized in the Controller of the MS files referenced from the mzIdentML and mzTab files.
    Author:
    Yasset Perez-Riverol, Rui Wang
